DomainFQDNDescription = Fully Qualified Domain Name (FQDN) must be specified
NamingPrefixDescription = Deployment prefix must be specified
ClusterNameDescription = Cluster must be specified
PhysicalMachineNamesDescription = Physical machine names must be specified
MissingHciOUName = No organizational unit (OU) specified in arguments or in configuration file.
MissingOURemediation = Create '{0}' organizational unit, or run deployment script.
HostsMissingRemediation = Create physical machine entries for ({0}) in '{1}', or run deployment script.
HostsWithIncorrectDnsNameRemediation = Change physical machine entries in the Computers OU to have a DNSHostName that contains the node name and DomainFQDN, or run deployment script.  Affected nodes: {0}
